description: Maskurbate likes to play games with hot straight dudes like Zack; that's why we're always thinking about new ways to make them do things they wouldn't normally do in a solo scene and still have fun at the same time. This time, we're playing Spin the Wheel! Our contestant has to perform the dare that the wheel stops on. Believe me, it takes a lot of guts for a straight guy to do some of those things! Congrats Zack, you're awesome! Enjoy our new game!
series: Spin The Wheel Zack! - Part One
title: Spin The Wheel Zack! - Part One, Scene #01
